ContentDesc_Omega: What if Omega's relentless testing had continued, and provided the elusive answer it sought? The minstrel's words invite you to imagine this scenario─to entertain the possibility of that which may have been─and follow the experiment to its ultimate conclusion.
Instancecontenttextdata_20100_Text: You are the Alpha, I am the Omega. <blip> Initiating direct analysis of subject group.
Instancecontenttextdata_20132_Text: <bleep> Pantokrator mode engaged. Rerouting logic resources to armament generation...
Instancecontenttextdata_20600_Text: I am the Omega and the Alpha. I will mimic your weakness to comprehend your strength.
Instancecontenttextdata_20603_Text: <blip> Diverting energy to party member generation. Testing efficacy of combat role allocation...
Instancecontenttextdata_20609_Text: Disengaging inhibitors to simulate improbable performance.
Instancecontenttextdata_20614_Text: Evaluation. Imitation of mortal form and behavior provides negligible improvement to combat capabilities.
Instancecontenttextdata_20615_Text: Final analysis. Drastic overhaul of combat logic required. Initiating reconfiguration sequence.
